trans-unit.source: Provides basic design-time functionality for ASP.NET server controls.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder grunnleggende utformingen funksjonalitet for ASP.NET-serverkontroller.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the DHTML behavior that is associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir DHTML virkemåten som er forbundet med designer.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.IHtmlControlDesignerBehavior"></xref> that is associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.IHtmlControlDesignerBehavior"> </xref> som er knyttet til designer.

trans-unit.source: Gets the data bindings collection for the current control.
trans-unit.target: Henter bindinger datainnsamlingen for gjeldende kontroll.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataBindingCollection"></xref> that contains the data bindings for the current control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataBindingCollection"> </xref> som inneholder databindingene for gjeldende kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Gets the design-time object representing the control that is associated with the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner"></xref> object on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Henter utformingen-objekt som representerer kontrollen som er knyttet til den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner"> </xref> objekt på utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: The DesignTimeElement property is used by the designer to retrieve the design-time object representing the control that is associated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner> object on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen DesignTimeElement brukes av designer til å hente utformingen-objekt som representerer kontrollen som er knyttet til den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner>objekt på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The design-time object representing the control associated with the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Utformingen-objekt som representerer kontrollen som er tilknyttet den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner"></xref> object and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner"> </xref> objekt og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose()` method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles av offentlig `Dispose()` metoden og <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`Aktiverer den beskyttede `Dispose(Boolean)` metoden med den `disposing` parameteren satt til `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>aktiverer `Dispose` med `disposing` satt til `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is `true`, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner> references.
trans-unit.target: Når den `disposing` parameteren er `true`, denne metoden Frigjør alle ressurser holdes av administrerte objekter som denne <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner>referanser.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden starter den `Dispose()` metode for hver referert objekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Gets the expression bindings for the current control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter uttrykksbindinger for gjeldende kontroll under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], uses the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder> class to get the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor> class to get the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet> to set expressions for control properties at design time.
trans-unit.target: Utformingen vert, for eksempel [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], bruker den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder>klassen for å få den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor>klassen for å få den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet>Angi uttrykk for egenskaper for kontroll på utformingstidspunktet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditor> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder>

trans-unit.source: Expression strings reference a localizable resource, an application setting, a connection string, or a custom expression type.
trans-unit.target: Uttrykket strenger referere til en lokaliserbare ressurs, en applikasjonsinnstilling, en tilkoblingsstreng eller en egendefinert uttrykk-type.

trans-unit.source: The Expressions collection contains an <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding> element for each control property that has an associated expression string.
trans-unit.target: Uttrykk-samlingen inneholder en <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding>element for hver kontrollegenskap som har en tilknyttet uttrykk-strengen.</xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.ExpressionPrefix%2A> property for each element indicates the associated expression builder implementation.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.ExpressionPrefix%2A>-egenskapen for hvert element angir tilknyttede uttrykket builder implementeringen.</xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.ExpressionPrefix%2A>

trans-unit.source: The expression string is parsed and evaluated by its associated <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder> to determine the control property value at run time.
trans-unit.target: Uttrykk-strengen er analysert og evalueres av de tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder>til fastsettes egenskapsverdien kontroll på kjøretidspunktet.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref> that contains the expressions strings set for properties in the current control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"> </xref> som inneholder uttrykkene strenger som er angitt for egenskapene i gjeldende kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the designer and sets the component for design.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer designer og angir komponenten for utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.Initialize%2A> method should be called by the designer host to initialize the designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.Initialize%2A>metoden må kalles av designer verten initialisere utformeren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: The control element for design.
trans-unit.target: Kontroll-elementet for utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Called when a behavior is associated with the element.
trans-unit.target: Kalles når en virkemåte er knyttet til elementet.

trans-unit.source: Called when a behavior disassociates from the element.
trans-unit.target: Kalles når en virkemåte disassociates fra elementet.

trans-unit.source: Provides a method that can be used to indicate when a data binding has changed.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en metode som kan brukes til å angi når en databinding er endret.

trans-unit.source: The OnBindingsCollectionChanged method should be called by a control designer after the control designer has made a change to the data bindings for the control.
trans-unit.target: OnBindingsCollectionChanged-metoden må kalles av en kontroll designer når kontrollen designer har endret til databindinger for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The OnBindingsCollectionChanged method is obsolete.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For OnBindingsCollectionChanged metoden er foreldet.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataBindingCollection.Changed> event on the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner.DataBindings%2A> collection for equivalent control designer functionality.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.DataBindingCollection.Changed>hendelse på den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner.DataBindings%2A>samling for tilsvarende kontrollere designer funksjonalitet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HtmlControlDesigner.DataBindings%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataBindingCollection.Changed>

trans-unit.source: The name of the property that has changed.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på egenskapen som er endret.

trans-unit.source: Provides a way to perform additional processing when the associated control is attached to a parent control.
trans-unit.target: Kan ikke utføre ytterligere behandling når den tilknyttede kontrollen er knyttet til en overordnet kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Sets the list of events that are exposed at design-time for the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor"></xref> object for the component.
trans-unit.target: Angir listen over hendelser som vises på utformingstidspunktet for den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor"> </xref> objekt for komponenten.

trans-unit.source: The PreFilterEvents method provides a way to add items to or remove items from the dictionary of events that a designer exposes through a <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden PreFilterEvents gjør det mulig å legge til eller fjerne elementer fra ordliste for hendelser som en designer viser via en <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>objektet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: The keys in the dictionary of events are the names of the events.
trans-unit.target: Nøkler i ordlisten for hendelser er navnene hendelser.

trans-unit.source: The objects are of type <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: Objektene er av typen <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> that contains the names of the events of the component to expose.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>som inneholder navn på hendelser av komponenten til å vise.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Allows the designer to expose a specific set of properties through a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor"></xref> object at design time.
trans-unit.target: Tillater utformeren for å vise et bestemt sett med egenskaper via en <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor"> </xref> objekt under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The PreFilterProperties method provides a way to add items to or remove items from the dictionary of properties that a designer exposes through a <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden PreFilterProperties gjør det mulig å legge til eller fjerne elementer fra liste over egenskaper som en designer viser via en <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>objektet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: The keys in the dictionary of properties are the names of the properties.
trans-unit.target: Nøkler i ordlisten for egenskaper er navnene på egenskapene.

trans-unit.source: The objects are of type <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: Objektene er av typen <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: The set of properties to filter for the component.
trans-unit.target: Settet med egenskaper for å filtrere for komponenten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether to create a field declaration for the control in the code-behind file for the current design document during serialization.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om du vil opprette en feltet deklarasjon for kontrollen i filen bakenforliggende kode for utformingsdokumentet under serialisering.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>, if a declaration should be created; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>, hvis en deklarasjon skal opprettes; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
